DeepSEA_annotations_investigations_Simons_WGS_1902

library(data.table)
library(ggplot2)
setwd("../../ASD/analysis/")
source("../lib/170117_gene_list_definition.R")

coding

HGMD_score <- list()
for(i in 1:6){
  file <- paste("../other_annotations/deepsea_annotations/web_retrieved_HGMD_scores/Simons_wgs_1902/jobs_", i, "/infile.vcf.out.snpclass", sep = "")
  temp <- fread(file, header = TRUE, sep = ",", stringsAsFactors = FALSE)
  HGMD_score <- append(HGMD_score, list(temp[,c("chr","pos","name", "HGMD-probability")]))
}



HGMD_score <- rbindlist(HGMD_score)

HGMD_score$start <- HGMD_score$pos - 1
HGMD_score$index <- seq(1,nrow(HGMD_score))


fwrite(HGMD_score[,c("chr","start","pos","index", "name","HGMD-probability")], "tmp/180615_temp.bed", col.names = FALSE, sep = "\t", row.names = FALSE, quote = FALSE)

command <- paste("../external_tools/bedtools-2.17.0/bin/bedtools intersect -a tmp/180615_temp.bed -b ../data/Example_windows_coding_with_nonfunctional_syn_mutrate_no_header.bed -wa -wb > tmp/180615_temp2.bed")

system(command)
